                </div>
                
                <h2>Building Long-Term Solutions</h2>
                <p>Creating lasting change requires consistent effort and cultural development:</p>
                
                <p><strong>Team Agreements:</strong> Work together to establish meeting norms that everyone commits to following.</p>
                <p><strong>Regular Check-ins:</strong> Periodically assess meeting effectiveness and adjust approaches as needed.</p>
                <p><strong>Training and Development:</strong> Provide communication and facilitation training for team members.</p>
                <p><strong>Lead by Example:</strong> Model the inclusive behavior you want to see in your meetings.</p>
